Author: gimmethatdamnavocado
Text: To more days of eating normally and hopefully feel less guilty 💪🏻💕

Author: hondaceviche
Text: Don't beat yourself up too much, you're right, you earned it. Willpower is a limited resource, sometimes we really do need to eat what we want and chill out for a day to maintain our sanity.  I ate like normal today too. Sometimes thems the breaks. Onward.
